      "content": "thanks. one thing though, the sound of the dripping is driving me crazy. it's like this constant tapping rhythm in the middle of the night. is there anything else that usually causes that kind of rhythmic noise besides just a bad washer? like maybe something stuck in the pipes or a pressure issue?",
